      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in pristine, showroom condition, reflecting meticulous care and an uncompromising commitment to excellence. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the untouched interior appointments, confirms its status as a premier acquisition for the discerning driver. Experience the pinnacle of performance and aesthetics in a vehicle that presents as new.",
      "price": 44800.0,
